[[!meta title="Numerous security holes in Tails 3.6.2"]]
[[!pagetemplate template="news.tmpl"]]

[[!tag security/fixed]]

Several security holes that affect Tails 3.6.2 are now fixed in Tails 3.7.

We **strongly** encourage you to
[[upgrade to Tails 3.7|news/version_3.7]] as soon as possible.

 - Tor Browser: [MSFA 2018-12](https://www.mozilla.org/en-US/security/advisories/mfsa2018-12/)
 - OpenSSL: [[!debsa2018 4157]]
 - Perl: [[!debsa2018 4172]]
 - Libre Office: [[!debsa2018 4178]]
 - libmad: [[!debsa2018 4192]]
